/**
 * Clinical Task Management System - Apps Script
 * 
 * This script handles:
 * 1. Access control (only task owners can edit)
 * 2. Auto-population of dates (Created, Updated, Last Outreach)
 * 3. Outreach tracking (auto-archive at 3rd attempt within 10 business days)
 * 4. Document completion (create clinician rows)
 * 5. Sorting (self-pay priority)
 * 6. Color formatting (status-based)
 * 7. Re-activation workflow
 * 
 * Instructions:
 * 1. Copy all code below
 * 2. Go to Tools > Script Editor in your Google Sheet
 * 3. Delete default code, paste this entire script
 * 4. Save (Ctrl+S)
 * 5. Click "Run" to authorize
 * 6. Set up triggers: Tools > Script Editor > Clock icon > Create new trigger
 */

